We get away from the threat of Be3 and are planning to go e5 and Be6.} (19...
Nc6 20. Rxb7 Bc8 21. Rb3 Nd4 22. Rb8 Nc6 23. Rb3 Nd4 24. Rb8 Nc6 25. Rb3 {
