{[%evp 0,11,-56,-13,-59,-39,-36,-33,-38,-31,-35,-47,-29,-22] How to continue
here?} 17... Ne8 $1 {A nice prophylactic move getting out of the potential pin.
The knight can be rerouted to the queenside.} 18. Bg5 (18. d5 Qd7 $11) (18. e5
cxd4 19. cxd4 Rd5 20. Qf3 (20. Qg4 Qd7 21. Re4 {runs into the strong} Ncd6 $1 {
